1	-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2	-- Company    : SLAC National Accelerator Laboratory
3	-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4	-- Description: Synchronizer Finite state machine
5	--              Finite state machine for sub-class 1 deterministic latency
6	--              lane synchronization.
7	--              It also supports sub-class 0 non deterministic mode.
8	-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
9	-- This file is part of 'SLAC Firmware Standard Library'.
